The Problem

B2B businesses need consistent client flow, but building internal sales teams is expensive, risky, and time-consuming.

Hiring is expensive & risky

SDR/BDR hiring costs $30-80k base salary without factoring in training, tools, management overhead, and ramp time. Most don't work out, and results aren't guaranteed.

Founders are stretched thin

You're already closing deals and delivering for clients. No bandwidth for prospecting, qualifying, and booking meetings.

Agencies deliver cold leads

Most agencies hand you contact info from a single channel and system. You still have to warm them up, qualify them, and book meetings yourself.

Growth is unpredictable

Feast or famine. Some months you're slammed, others you're scrambling for pipeline. No consistent system.
